attachments.title: A T-Rex Is Running a Dungeons & Dragons Game on Twitter, and It's Even More Epic Than It Sounds
attachments.text: Sometimes, the world can feel like a scary and confusing place. There are forces beyond our control. We feel helpless and small. Then, a Tyrannosaurus Rex plays Dungeons & Dragons, and suddenly, the world makes sense again.
